dct_title_s: Map of Agra City and cantonments
dct_description_sm: Harrison & Sons. Companion text: Three days at Agra: a guide to places of interest, including Fath'pur Sikri, with history and map / Herbert Andrews Newell. London: Harrison and Sons. 1920. 121p. Name of publisher has been cut off: "Harrison & --------- Lane, W.C." Map Library does not have the guide that accompanies this map.
